{"article_id":"x7i9PTGj7UMIXLnB","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Republican lawmakers are fuming over a bombshell report overnight","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"that the U.S. government airlifted the equivalent of $ 400 million to Iran this past January","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"- as four detained Americans were released by Tehran -","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"and say","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"the transaction has put more Americans at risk","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"of being taken hostage .","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"The cash transfer ,","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"as reported by The Wall Street Journal ,","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"was the first installment","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"paid in a $ 1.7 billion settlement","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"the Obama administration reached with Iran","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"to resolve a failed 1979 arms deal","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"dating from just before the Iranian Revolution .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"The cash","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"flown to Iran","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"consisted of euros , Swiss francs , and other currencies","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"because U.S. law forbids transacting American dollars with Iran .","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"While the Obama administration denied","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"the cash transfer was done","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"to secure the release of the four Americans ,","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"GOP lawmakers said","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"it was tantamount to \" ransom . \"","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"`` Paying ransom to kidnappers puts Americans even more at risk , ''","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"Sen. Mark Kirk , R-Ill. , said in a statement .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"`` While Americans were relieved by Iran ' s overdue release of illegally imprisoned American hostages ,","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"the White House ' s policy of appeasement has led Iran to illegally seize more American hostages . ''","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"The four released Americans are Washington Post reporter Jason Rezaian ; Amir Hekmati , a former U.S. Marine ; Christian pastor Saeed Abedini ; and Nosratollah Khosravi-Roodsari ,","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"whose case had not been publicized before the release .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"State Department spokesman John Kirby said","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"their release was on an entirely separate track from the settlement payment","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"and , in an interview Wednesday with , said","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"any suggestion","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"it was tied to ransom","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"is \" utterly false . \"","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"\" We just don ' t pay ransom . ...","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"This was not ransom , \"","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Kirby further said","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"there was \" no secret \" about the payment .","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"\" It was their money , \"","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"Kirby told ,","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"noting","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"the funds had been frozen","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"and it \" made no sense for us to continue to drag out their claim. \"","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"He argued","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"the \" compromise \"","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"struck with Iran","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"worked to the \" taxpayers ' benefit \"","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"because potentially billions more could have been on the line .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"In a written statement , Kirby said","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"the negotiations over the Americans and over the settlement were even conducted `` by different teams on each side . ''","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"He said :","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"`` The funds","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"that were transferred to Iran","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"were related solely to the settlement of a long-standing claim at the U.S.-Iran Claims Tribunal at The Hague . ''","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"However , the Journal says","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"U.S. officials acknowledge","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"that Iranian negotiators on the prisoner exchange said","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"they wanted the cash","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"to show","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"they had gained something tangible .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"The Journal also reported","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"that President Obama did not disclose the $ 400 million cash payment","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"when he announced Jan. 17","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"that the arms deal dispute had been resolved .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"The administration has not disclosed","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"how the $ 1.7 billion was paid ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"except to say","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"it was not paid in dollars .","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"\" The logistics of this payment","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"-- literally delivering a plane full of cash","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"to evade U.S. law --","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"shows yet again the extraordinary lengths","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"the Obama administration will go","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"to accommodate Iran ,","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"all while hiding the facts from Congress and the American people , \"","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"House Foreign Affairs Committee Chairman Ed Royce , R-Calif. , said in a statement .","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"\" Hundreds of millions in the pockets of a terrorist regime means a more dangerous region , period .","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"And paying ransom only puts more American lives in jeopardy . \"","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"Since the cash was airlifted ,","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"Iran 's Revolutionary Guard has arrested two more Iranian-Americans .","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"Tehran also has detained dual-nationals from France , Canada and the U.K. in recent months .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":163,"left":87,"right":162,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":84,"right":86,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":84,"left":0,"right":83,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":83,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":86,"left":3,"right":85,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":85,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":97,"right":161,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":93,"right":96,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":88,"right":92,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":88,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":8,"right":91,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":9,"right":90,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":10,"right":89,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":89,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":94,"right":95,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":94,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":161,"left":105,"right":160,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":99,"right":104,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":99,"left":17,"right":98,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":98,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":100,"right":103,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":103,"left":101,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":22,"right":23,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":24,"right":25,"relat